  "detailed_description": "<h1>YOU MAY ALSO LIKE</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>I Love Finding Cats & Pups is a classic hidden object game set in beautiful scenes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463710/extras/b8f20dd1edb8824b3dc715652a7b554f.poster.avif?t=1721094578\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463710/extras/b8f20dd1edb8824b3dc715652a7b554f.webm?t=1721094578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463710/extras/b8f20dd1edb8824b3dc715652a7b554f.mp4?t=1721094578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Search through them all to adopt and collect all the pawsome cats and pups! Play new mini games, solve fun puzzles, and collect all the adorable cats & pups!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463710/extras/982073eb62804b8dff6ea4c2f619636b.poster.avif?t=1721094578\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463710/extras/982073eb62804b8dff6ea4c2f619636b.webm?t=1721094578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463710/extras/46bfcf0b96063f8504bbccabaeb14d32.poster.avif?t=1721094578\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463710/extras/46bfcf0b96063f8504bbccabaeb14d32.webm?t=1721094578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2463710/extras/46bfcf0b96063f8504bbccabaeb14d32.mp4?t=1721094578\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find a great variety of cats and pups!<br></li><li>Explore beautiful hidden object locations. <br></li><li>Play over 20 fun mini games!<br></li><li>Collect and adopt all the adorable cats and pups!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collector’s Edition</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>6 extra locations<br></li><li>12 minigames<br></li><li>A set of wallpapers<br></li><li>Music player.<br></li><li>Additional cats and pups that can’t wait to meet you!<br></li><li>Meet the developers’ cats and pups!</li></ul>",
